    <string name="settings_dot_search_screen_title">Drawer dot search</string>
    <string name="settings_dot_search_explanation">In the app drawer, type a dot and a space, then your search words. For a shortcut, use a dot, one lowercase letter, a space, then your search (for example `.a coffee`). The app list only includes apps that expose web search or standard in-app search for their package. For other sites or apps, add an HTTPS URL or deep link template and put %1$s where the search text belongs (for example https://example.com/search?q=%1$s).</string>
